Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:51.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Life was given to us a billion years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:53.92,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What have we done with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as easy as pie. In and out, all done and dusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:21.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The last thing the guy is expecting is a total 10 turning up to deliver the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll blow his mind. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:24.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweetheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:29.69,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get paranoid on me, alright? You trust me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:42.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard, I really do like you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've to take care of myself right now, I got a...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.89,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, I gotta concentrate on so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home because I have exams on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:56.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to shower and I have to study, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:03:00.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what? The other day I was in this museum and you know what I found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The first ever woman was named Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that suppose to make me feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- No.  - I'll call you, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! OK! OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be honest with you. I can't deliver the case myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've a little falling out with the guy. It's nothing major...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but if it's you, problem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You walk in there, you go up to the reception,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,you ask Mr. Jang to come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:33.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He comes down, he takes the case, you flash him your prettiest smile and bounce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you can even see the reception from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:43.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's in the case?  - I don't know, it's just some paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah? Let's see it then.  - It's locked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and no one but Mr. Jang has the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just the delivery boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you get paid to do this?  - Yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, we're negotiating now or ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, how much do you get paid? I want to know, how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:06.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You get paid a thousand dollars for delivering paperwork, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:10.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, it takes me 10 minutes and they're paying a grand and the rest is none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not my business either. I'll tell you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Listen!  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We split it down the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 500 for you and 500 for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:23.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Richard, I will call you.  - Listen! It is the third time this week
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:26.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm showing up at the same hotel with the same cowboy hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Problem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go! Go! I'll wait for you to go.  - Lucy, honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I've done this a dozen times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:38.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's paperwork! It's probably just some designs they swept so they can copy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it works in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:41.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my Stetson was made here. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:44.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It says so on the label: "Made in Taiwan"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, cowboy, with a fake Stetson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What the hell are you doing?  - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What the hell are you do...  - I'm so sorry. I really need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it! Take this off me, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can't!  - Take this off me, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can't! Mr. Jang is the only one who has the key!  - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to is go into the hotel and ask for him at the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Take it off me, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, I really have no choice. The sooner you go in, the sooner you'll be back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you did this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.89,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'll be right here, you have my word.  - Your word isn't worth shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... it's worth 500 bucks, upfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're wonderful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here for, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who should I say is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:01.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... no... Richard sent... Richard sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:18.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard's... uh... he's just looking for a place to park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang still wants to know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:38.60,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Lucy. If he could... If he could he quick 'cause I have... I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second while I translate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang is on his way, stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:56.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang said you need to stay right here. I think it's better if you stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Regent Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.60,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything! Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.21,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:14.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Tambien hablo poco Espanol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, yes, I'm Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just been a terrible mistake. I'm just suppose to deliver this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:41.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lost the key, you don't have to chop off my hand, you can just cut the chain, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:47.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:53.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Miss, I speak English. I translate for Mr. Jang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:31.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell him that I haven't done anything. I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all just a big mistake, OK? Please, please tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, OK, OK, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:49.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang wants to know what's in the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:52.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know what's in the case. Do you speak English or don't you speak English?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:56.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do! I studied one year at International High School in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:03.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard gave me the case to give to you, that's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, please tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me a paper with numbers written on it, I don't... what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the code to open the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's really in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So why won't he open it himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't trust Mr. Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.29,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust Richard either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I only dated him for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.60,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! OK! OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Jang insists that you open the case.  - OK! OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:21.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please God, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:33.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants you to hurry up, Mr. Jang has other things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.60,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you describe the content of the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 4 plastic pouches filled with blue powder like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:15.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe a purple powder? I don't know, it looks gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang wants to offer you a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.25,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:52.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If life starts approximately a billion years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to wait 400,000 years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:57.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to see the aberration of the first nerve cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:00.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where life we know it begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Brains in formation of only a few milligrams
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:09.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,is not possible to determine any sign of intelligence yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It acts more as a reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:17.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,One neuron, you're alive. Two neurons, you're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:21.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And with movement, interesting things begin to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Animal life on Earth goes back millions of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:36.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, most species only use 3-5% of its cerebral capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:40.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't until we reached human beings at the top of the animal chain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:45.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that we finally see a species used more of its cerebral capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:53.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,10% may not seem like much but it's a lot if we look at all we've done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's discuss a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:35.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The only living being that uses its brain better than us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's estimated that this incredible animal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:45.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,uses up to 20% of its cerebral capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:52.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And in particular, this allows it to have an echo-location system
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:57.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that's more efficient than any sonar invented by mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:01.74,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But the dolphin did not invent the sonar. It developed it naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:06.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the crucial part of our
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:09.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,philosophical reflection we have today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we therefore conclude
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that humans are concerned more with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"having"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,than "being".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:19.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with my stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:25.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Just a little horizontal slit. It's very well done
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll find that in a month, this scar is practically invisible too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:33.59,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to show your tummy off on the beach next summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it, uh... is it why we opened you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:44.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, we didn't harvest your organs or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:48.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we merely slipped a little package in your lower tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:52.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a... it's a new drug the kids in Europe are gonna love, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:57.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is it?  - Well, the scientific term is CPH4,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,which is not very sexy from a sale's point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:03.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh... we're... we're still working on something a little bit more pop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:05.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Any suggestions?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:10.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, come on in. Lovely, oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid! Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous! Lovely lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- How are you?  - Very good, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:33.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, uh... first of all, many thanks for taking part in this enterprise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,which I'm sure will go off flawlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,These lovely passport and tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:41.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,will enable you to return home in the next 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:45.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, upon arrival, you'll be taken in hand by our people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,so that we might recover our merchandise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:52.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and you might re-discover the freedom which you so richly deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:57.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I don't need to remind you but, for any of those who may be tempted to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:02.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,warn or turn themselves in to the authorities,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:09.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,we have the names and addresses of the families of every one of you down to the distant cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:15.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we rely therefore, on your complete discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, anyway, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:22.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,gentleman, madam, allow me to be the first to wish you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna sell this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid it's our business model.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:44.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,For primitive beings like us, life seems to only have one single purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaining time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:51.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And its going through time, seems to be also the only
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,real purpose of each of the cell in our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To achieve that aim, the mass of the cells
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:22:00.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that make up earthworm and human beings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,has only 2 solutions:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,be immortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:06.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,or to reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:11.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If its habitat is not sufficiently favourable or nurturing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:21.15,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the cell will choose immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:25.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, self-sufficiency and self-management.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, if the habitat is favourable,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.44,0:22:36.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,they will choose to reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:48.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, when they die,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:51.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,they hand down essential information and knowledge to the next cell
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:54.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,which hands it down to the next cell and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, knowledge and learning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:11.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,are handed down through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:15.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK, keep calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:18.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to wait, just play for time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:20.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have time to think it through on the plane... just take the flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:22.69,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,take the flight, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:25.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the main thing right now, just save time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:28.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try anything, keep your cool, you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:31.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,you're alive... you're alive, that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:33.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, save time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Save time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.62,0:24:10.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.23,0:26:10.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's imagine for a few moments
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.27,0:26:13.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,what our life would be like if we could access, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.07,0:26:17.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,20 % of our brains' capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.41,0:26:22.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This first stage would give us access to and control
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.11,0:26:23.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,of our own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.90,0:26:25.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sir.  - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.22,0:26:27.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it been proven scientifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.85,0:26:31.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for the moment, it's just hypothesis, I confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.70,0:26:33.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.83,0:26:38.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,it's troubling to realize that the Greeks, the Egyptians and the Indians
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:43.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,had notion of "cells" centuries before the invention of the microscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.48,0:26:45.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And what to say about Darwin
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.44,0:26:49.60,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,whom everybody took for a fool when he put forward his Theory of Evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.66,0:26:52.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to us to push the rules and laws
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.22,0:26:56.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and go from "evolution" to "revolution".
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.51,0:27:01.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,100 billion neurons per human,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.44,0:27:04.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,of which only 15% are activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.33,0:27:09.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There're more connections in the human body than there're stars in the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.66,0:27:13.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We possess a gigantic network of information
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.73,0:27:16.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to which we've almost no access.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.08,0:27:19.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sir!  - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.66,0:27:21.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And what would be the next stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.45,0:27:25.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the next stage would probably be control of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.77,0:27:30.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But for that, we will need to access at least 40% of our brains' capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.11,0:27:34.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And after control of ourselves and others,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.55,0:27:37.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,come control of matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.11,0:27:41.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we're entering the realm of science fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.22,0:27:45.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't know anything more than a dog who watches the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.48,0:27:47.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Excuse me, sir.  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.33,0:27:50.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But what would happen if for some reason we ignore
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.77,0:27:54.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,somebody unlock 100% of the celebral capacity?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.02,0:27:57.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,100%?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.67,0:27:58.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.55,0:28:03.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:36.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.28,0:30:49.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, you speak English?  - No. No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.27,0:30:52.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You speak English? - Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.12,0:30:54.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Take me to the hospital now.  - Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.57,0:31:45.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hospital.  - Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.69,0:32:34.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.78,0:32:37.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:40.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need help, it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.24,0:32:42.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot be in here. We're operating.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.33,0:32:44.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.91,0:33:05.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be able to save him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.44,0:33:08.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Tumour already invaded the cortext and right side of his spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.34,0:33:13.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody put a bag of drug in me. I need you to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.00,0:33:15.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's leaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.13,0:33:19.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.78,0:33:23.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'll just administer local anaethestic...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.20,0:33:24.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.83,0:33:27.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.33,0:33:32.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, please. Put the gun down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.40,0:33:35.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to... examine, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.03,0:33:41.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you mind?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.09,0:33:51.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello?  - Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.95,0:33:54.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.26,0:33:56.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's great to hear from you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.66,0:33:58.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but what time is it over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.62,0:34:01.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. It's night.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.96,0:34:04.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec', let me get rid of the other line.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.11,0:34:07.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.12,0:34:09.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, you're not partying too much, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.86,0:34:12.71,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me you'll look after yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.77,0:34:15.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to, Mommy, I'm trying to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.68,0:34:19.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks for calling out of the blue like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.81,0:34:21.60,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is gonna be sad he missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.79,0:34:26.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't home from the gym yet. Usually you call us in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.15,0:34:28.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mom...  - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.82,0:34:30.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.44,0:34:32.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, sweatie?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.28,0:34:37.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Space,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.88,0:34:39.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.33,0:34:45.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the vibrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.66,0:34:48.20,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.50,0:34:52.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.33,0:34:56.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the rotation of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.77,0:35:00.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat leaving my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.19,0:35:04.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the blood in my veins,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.88,0:35:07.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.50,0:35:11.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The deepest parts of my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:16.21,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweatie, we've a bad connection, I can't hear you so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.25,0:35:18.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say about "memory"?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:24.69,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain in my mouth, when I had braces, I ...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.77,0:35:30.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can remember the feeling of your hand on my forehead when I ran a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.22,0:35:34.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember stroking the cat. It was so soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.31,0:35:37.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat? What cat, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.87,0:35:40.74,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Siamese with blue eye and a broken tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.77,0:35:43.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweatie, you can't possibly remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.53,0:35:45.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You were barely a year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.23,0:35:52.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember the days of your milk in my mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.43,0:35:54.89,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.80,0:35:57.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the liquid...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.73,0:36:03.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweatie, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.15,0:36:08.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanna tell you that I love you, Mom and Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.09,0:36:10.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweatie...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.80,0:36:13.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanna thank you for the...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.16,0:36:17.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,thousand kisses that I can still feel on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.25,0:36:22.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.23,0:36:24.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too, sweatie,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:27.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,more than anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.98,0:36:37.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How much is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.48,0:36:40.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,500 grams?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.99,0:36:44.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And how long will it take for my body to eliminate the rest of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.11,0:36:50.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To answer that, I need to know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.39,0:36:51.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.58,0:36:52.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.69,0:36:55.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,CPH4.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.00,0:37:00.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.44,0:37:06.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Pregnant women manufacture CPH4 in the sixth week of pregnancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.79,0:37:09.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,in tiny quantities.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.41,0:37:14.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,For a baby, it packs the power of an atomic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.25,0:37:19.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what gives the foetus the necessary energy to form all the bones in its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:22.59,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard they tried to make a synthetic version of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.69,0:37:25.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't realize that they succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.71,0:37:28.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If it really is CPH4,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.40,0:37:31.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,in this quantity, I'm amazed you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.61,0:37:34.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.81,0:39:43.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Learning is always a painful process.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.77,0:39:46.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when you're little, your bones are growing and you ached all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.22,0:39:51.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe I can remember the sound of my own bones growing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.54,0:39:55.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this grinding under the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.33,0:39:57.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.05,0:40:01.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Like... sound of music that I can understand, like fluids...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.17,0:40:05.74,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny I used to be so concerned with
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.90,0:40:09.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,who I was and what I wanted to be, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.91,0:40:14.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,now I've access to the furthest reaches of my brain, I see things clearly and realize
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.68,0:40:17.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,what make us "us", it's primitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.79,0:40:20.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.30,0:40:22.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that make any sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.00,0:40:26.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this pain you're experiencing...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.34,0:40:28.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,is blocking you from understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.87,0:40:31.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All you know now is pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.56,0:40:33.29,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you know, pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.33,0:40:38.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.94,0:40:41.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The others carrying the drugs. I need the rest of it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.90,0:40:43.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,for medicinal purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.12,0:41:15.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.71,0:41:21.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.37,0:41:29.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.99,0:41:36.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.16,0:41:53.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, good evening, Professor.  - I sweared I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.92,0:41:55.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You hadn't forget your dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.57,0:41:58.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid so. I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.00,0:42:00.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Have a good rest.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.75,0:42:08.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared the shit out of me. You ring that bell like some nut bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.76,0:42:11.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.61,0:42:14.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.93,0:42:17.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose your key or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.74,0:42:18.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.64,0:42:22.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Can I borrow your laptop?  - Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.44,0:42:25.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So I spent all day at this audition, awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.44,0:42:30.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They just have you standing around all day because they don't give a shit about your time, gabbing away in Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.80,0:42:33.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who understand Chinese? I don't understand Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.74,0:42:35.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And then they say they always gonna call
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.05,0:42:38.15,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and they never do. They don't even take your phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.17,0:42:41.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know.Except this one guy, I bet he, uh...he's not Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.03,0:42:45.60,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He works at the agency and he's cute... Oh my God, he's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.68,0:42:49.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like, the cute in kinda way, like he has this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.27,0:42:51.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God, his ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.88,0:42:53.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get started on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.39,0:42:55.60,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll never gonna guess where he take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.69,0:43:01.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Four Seasons, Royal Suite, and we made love all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.88,0:43:05.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm talking about myself. What's up? How's Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.66,0:43:06.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.84,0:43:09.74,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are crazy. I'm gonna take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.41,0:43:23.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes?  - Profesor Norman, my name is Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.61,0:43:26.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just read all your research on the human's brain. We need to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.22,0:43:30.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my research?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.54,0:43:35.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm very flattered, young lady. But I find that hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.91,0:43:37.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have written no less than...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.32,0:43:41.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,6734 pages. I can recite them too all by heart if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.70,0:43:47.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of Emily's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.40,0:43:51.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This sounds like one of her silly jokes. Is she there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.71,0:43:53.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.66,0:43:58.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who are you?  - I just told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.66,0:44:03.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, right? Yes, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.24,0:44:05.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I read your theory on the use of the brain's capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.86,0:44:08.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little rudimentary but you're on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.66,0:44:10.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.01,0:44:14.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, my cells are reproducing at a phenomenal speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.23,0:44:15.59,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,several millions per second,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.79,0:44:19.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm having trouble precisely evaluating the time of my death
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.05,0:44:21.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but I doubt it'll last more than 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.62,0:44:23.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.12,0:44:26.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is that your theory is not a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.36,0:44:30.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I absorbed a large quatity of synthetic CPH4
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.77,0:44:33.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that would allow me to use 100% of my celebral capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.00,0:44:37.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm at 28% and which you wrote is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.40,0:44:41.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the brain reaches 20% , it opens up and expands the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.44,0:44:43.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and there are no more obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.11,0:44:46.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They fall away like dominos. I'm colonizing my own brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.68,0:44:53.71,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... well... I don't know... what to... say.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.66,0:44:59.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, I've... I've been working on this theory for over 20 years but it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.68,0:45:05.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,it's only... all ever been hypothesis and research ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.40,0:45:08.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I never thought anyone would...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.88,0:45:12.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You can control your own metabolism?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.01,0:45:13.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.49,0:45:16.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can start to control other people's bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.61,0:45:20.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Also I can control magnetic and electric waves and...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.43,0:45:23.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,not all of them, just... the most basic.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.12,0:45:25.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Television.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.22,0:45:27.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.66,0:45:30.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.35,0:45:35.71,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.04,0:45:40.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.33,0:45:42.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.59,0:45:44.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.62,0:45:49.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like all things that make us human are fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.55,0:45:55.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the less human I feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.38,0:46:00.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,all these knowledge about... everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.17,0:46:03.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Quantum Physics, Applied Mathemathics,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.88,0:46:07.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the infinite capacity of the cell's nucleus,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.16,0:46:11.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all exploding inside my brain, all these knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.33,0:46:14.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.73,0:46:19.92,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're asking me... what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.97,0:46:30.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.93,0:46:34.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.44,0:46:37.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the very nature of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.31,0:46:41.20,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, from the very begining...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.40,0:46:48.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The development of the first cell... divided into two cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.02,0:46:52.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole purpose of life has been
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.71,0:46:57.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,passed on what was learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.63,0:47:01.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no higher purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.44,0:47:06.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you're asking me what to do with all these knowledge you're accumalating, I'd say...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.55,0:47:10.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.10,0:47:16.59,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like any simple cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.91,0:47:18.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,going through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.88,0:47:21.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.52,0:47:23.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.74,0:47:28.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be at your door in 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.37,0:47:39.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- You leaving?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.16,0:47:44.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is this?  - A prescription.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.93,0:47:47.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you start writing Chinese?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.26,0:47:50.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Since an hour ago.  - Lucy, I don't understand any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.32,0:47:54.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your kidneys aren't functioning efficiently. Your liver is failing. You need to make some lifestyle changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.83,0:47:57.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this medication. Work out. Eat organic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.77,0:47:59.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.63,0:48:09.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, at 11 p.m., a woman shot a patient dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.93,0:48:40.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Del Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.55,0:48:52.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello ?  - Yes, I've important imformation about a group of drug traffickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.83,0:48:55.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to speak with someone in position of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.29,0:49:00.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-hah, you're very lucky. There's no one with more authority in this office than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.06,0:49:02.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's start with the begining. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.25,0:49:06.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Pierre Del Rio, get off your desk, sit in your chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.11,0:49:09.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,pick up the red pen to your left and take down everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.55,0:49:18.71,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There're no cameras, hurry up. I've no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.94,0:49:27.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.97,0:49:31.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be sending you details of three people about to arrive in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.33,0:49:35.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Each one is carrying a kilo of drugs. I need you to arrest them and collect the substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.46,0:49:36.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.70,0:49:39.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What form of these drugs in? Bars? Capsules?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.68,0:49:43.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Powder, hidden in plastic pouches inside their intestines.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.66,0:49:44.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.66,0:49:47.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to be careful when you remove them. The product is very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.52,0:49:55.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.19,0:49:58.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.70,0:49:59.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.11,0:50:01.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.12,0:50:03.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.31,0:51:37.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.18,0:51:56.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Del Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.46,0:51:58.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for calling me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.95,0:52:00.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We got the third guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.33,0:52:03.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks very much. I'll send you the paper work with the transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.48,0:52:05.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.75,0:52:16.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, we're now beginning our descend to Paris-Charles de Gaulle.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.77,0:52:27.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, I've to ask you to put away your computer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.35,0:52:29.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You should wipe your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.21,0:52:31.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Excuse me?  - May I have a glass of champagne?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.44,0:52:34.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.86,0:52:55.89,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, your champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.13,0:52:58.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.76,0:53:02.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry but... uh, you really need to close your table now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.04,0:53:04.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.07,0:53:15.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.53,0:53:29.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If the habitat is not sufficiently favorable or nurturing...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.21,0:53:41.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,the cell will choose immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.03,0:53:50.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In another word, self-sufficiency and self-management.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.59,0:54:08.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, miss, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.05,0:54:11.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You must remain seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.94,0:54:13.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.20,0:54:19.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.55,0:54:24.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, open the door! You really have to go back to your seat! Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.93,0:54:26.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to land soon, please, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.71,0:54:30.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, say something, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.88,0:54:31.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.04,0:54:34.92,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.43,0:54:38.20,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, please open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.50,0:54:44.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, help me open!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.85,0:54:56.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.51,0:55:09.20,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss? Are you okay? Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.40,0:56:24.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.06,0:56:28.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I need to talk to you alone.  - And I need you to put your hands up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.96,0:56:51.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get the packets?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.22,0:56:54.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.04,0:56:57.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where're they?  - They're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.23,0:57:00.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.54,0:57:02.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be safer in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.26,0:57:33.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, as a cop, we see some pretty weird shit
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.49,0:57:36.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've to be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.27,0:57:38.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What you did back there, that freaked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.47,0:57:41.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To put everyone to sleep like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.72,0:57:43.75,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,do I need to be worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.04,0:57:45.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.51,0:57:47.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.29,0:58:10.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.47,0:58:12.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.10,0:58:33.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's that?  - Korean, I'm going to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.96,0:58:36.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Hey! No! No! No! This is a police car!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.90,0:58:39.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! No, this is not possible, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.76,0:58:41.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a police car!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.40,0:58:44.75,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.36,0:59:00.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, sir, excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.86,0:59:02.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.36,0:59:07.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm a German citizen and I demand us a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.22,0:59:40.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always drive like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.77,0:59:42.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I never driven before.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.73,0:59:43.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.56,0:59:52.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, this is one way!  - We're late.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.83,1:00:15.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I would rather be late than dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.52,1:00:16.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We never really die.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.77,1:01:09.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sir, I don't agree...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.55,1:01:18.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.53,1:01:33.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell them to stop following us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.04,1:01:34.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.93,1:02:58.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.88,1:04:09.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.65,1:04:24.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.85,1:04:27.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I could be of any help for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.08,1:04:33.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.21,1:04:35.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.77,1:04:43.34,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A reminder.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.06,1:04:45.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.66,1:05:14.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.94,1:05:16.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the first left.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.73,1:05:19.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.06,1:05:43.29,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Professor?  - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.29,1:05:44.92,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes?  - Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.21,1:05:46.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her, it's her.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.77,1:05:49.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, you're in Paris?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.46,1:05:50.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.51,1:05:52.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good, excellant.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.63,1:05:57.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So, look, I'm no longer at the hotel now, uh, I've come to the university
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.42,1:06:02.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,where I've taken the liberty of calling and gathering a few of my colleagues to discuss your case.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.04,1:06:05.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Top men in their field and um... very trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.46,1:06:06.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.80,1:06:10.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you. So, do you think you can meet us here at the university?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.02,1:06:18.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm, uh...I'm very pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.45,1:06:20.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.16,1:06:22.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Captain Del Rio.  - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.43,1:06:27.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let... let me introduce you to my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.37,1:06:29.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Professor Cartier, neuro surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.84,1:06:31.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Professor...  - I know who everyone is.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.29,1:06:34.75,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.77,1:06:39.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, gentlemen, this is Lucy, the first woman to...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.26,1:06:42.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... like I mentioned earlier...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.88,1:06:46.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Lucy has for reasons, remains a mystery to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.50,1:06:50.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,unlocked certain portion of her brain
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.33,1:06:51.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,that offered access
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.88,1:06:55.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to... previously unexplored celebral zones.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.66,1:06:59.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She has abilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.66,1:07:01.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give us an example?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.37,1:07:04.73,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter, Gabriel, aged 6, died in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.80,1:07:07.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a blue car, leather seats...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.16,1:07:09.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,plastic bird hanging from the rear view mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.87,1:07:52.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There're men coming here, can you secure the room?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.83,1:07:55.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I need to stay focus.  - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.72,1:08:02.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Speed it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.17,1:08:14.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you manage to access all these information?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.39,1:08:16.21,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Electrical impulses...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.22,1:08:19.25,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Every cell knows and talks to every other cell.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.30,1:08:22.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They exchange a thousand bits of information between them per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.63,1:08:25.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cells group together, forming a giant web of communication
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.24,1:08:28.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,which in turn forms matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.01,1:08:32.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cells get together, take on one form,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.54,1:08:34.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,deform, reform,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.55,1:08:36.75,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,makes no difference, it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.55,1:08:39.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Human considers themself unique.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.48,1:08:43.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they rooted their whole theory of existence on their uniqueness.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.19,1:08:46.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"One"... is the unit of measure but it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.36,1:08:49.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All social systems we put into place are mere "sketch".
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.54,1:08:52.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,1 + 1 = 2 That's all we learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.30,1:08:55.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But 1 + 1 has never equalled 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.50,1:08:58.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in fact, no numbers and no letters.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.56,1:09:02.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We codify our existence to bring it down to human size
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.06,1:09:04.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,to make it comprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.11,1:09:09.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We created the scale so that we can forget its unfathomable scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.33,1:09:14.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But if humans are not the unit of measure,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.06,1:09:17.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and the world isn't governed by mathemathical laws,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.02,1:09:20.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,what governs all that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.36,1:09:24.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Form a car speeding down the road...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.56,1:09:27.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,speed up the image infinitely
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.89,1:09:29.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,and the car disappears.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.54,1:09:35.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what proof do we have of its existence?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.81,1:09:38.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Time gives legitimacy to its existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.15,1:09:41.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is the only true unit of meassure.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.74,1:09:44.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It gives proof to the existence of matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.00,1:09:46.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Without time,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.53,1:09:49.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.43,1:09:57.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is "unity".
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.28,1:10:13.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't be able to hold them for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.49,1:10:16.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go then.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.19,1:10:32.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you need such huge doses?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.24,1:10:33.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid you won't survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.72,1:10:37.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Some cells inside me will fight and defend their integrity to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.91,1:10:41.36,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to attain the last few percent, I've to force it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.72,1:10:44.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To crack the cells open to their nucleus.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.35,1:10:55.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All these knowledge, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.33,1:11:00.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure that mankind is ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.32,1:11:02.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so driven by power and profit.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.33,1:11:05.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Given man's nature,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.40,1:11:09.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,it might bring us only instability and chaos.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.86,1:11:16.29,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignorance brings chaos, not knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.44,1:11:19.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll build a computer and download all my knowledge in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.76,1:11:22.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a way for you to have access to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.29,1:11:24.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.95,1:11:28.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope, we'll be worthy of your sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.68,1:11:39.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.23,1:11:59.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand English?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.33,1:13:02.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.66,1:13:05.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She's looking for energy and matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.37,1:13:12.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's trying to connect with our computers.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.93,1:14:17.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.49,1:14:30.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she making?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.37,1:14:32.95,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A new generation of computer, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.49,1:21:04.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.39,1:21:23.92,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the computer, it's moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.29,1:21:51.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.35,1:21:53.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.61,1:22:25.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Life was given to us a billion years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.03,1:22:28.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you know what to do with it.
